# example config
MaildirStore local
Path ~/mail/migadu/
SubFolders Verbatim
Inbox ~/mail/migadu/Inbox
Trash Trash

IMAPStore migadu
SSLType IMAPS
Host imap.migadu.com
Port 993
User username@example.com
Pass hunter2
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

Channel migadu
Master :migadu:
Slave :local:
SyncState *
Patterns * INBOX
Create Both
Expunge Both
Sync All
